PROGRAM GrilledCheeseSandwich
  Turn on stovetop to medium heat
  Place 1 pat of butter in pan
  Place pan on stovetop
  Take 1 slice of bread from rye loaf
  Place slice of bread on cutting board
  Squirt 1 tablespoon of mustard onto slice
  3 TIMES DO
    Place slice of cheese onto bread
  END
  Take 1 slice of bread from loaf
  Squirt 1 tablespoon of mustard onto slice
  Place slice of bread on top, mustard-side down
  The 2 slices of bread, mustard and 3 slices of cheese are now a sandwich
  Push spatula under sandwich
  Place sandwich in pan
  BreadFlipped = FALSE
  WHILE (bottom of bread not golden yellow && crispy) DO
    Wait 30 seconds
    Lift bottom of bread with spatula and check bread
  END
  IF (BreadFlipped == FALSE)
    Flip the sandwich over
    BreadFlipped = TRUE
  END
  WHILE (bottom of bread not golden yellow && crispy) DO
    Wait 30 seconds
    Lift bottom of bread with spatula and check bread
  END
  Using spatula, move sandwich to plate
  Turn off burner
  IF (sandwich is cool enough to touch)
    Eat sandwich
  ELSE
    Wait 2 minutes
    Eat sandwich
  END
END